单行文字溢出
```scss
{
    width: 200px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
}
```

多行文字溢出

```scss
{
    width: 200px;
    overflow : hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
}
```

超长文本整块省略

```html
<section>
    <p class="person-card__desc">
        <span>FE</span>
        <span>UI</span>
        <span>UX Designer</span>
        <span>前端工程师</span>
    </p>
</section>
```

```scss
.person-card__desc {
    width: 200px;
    white-space: normal;
    overflow : hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 1;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
}
.person-card__desc span {
    display: inline-block;
}
```
